{"id":1734523,"retrievedAt":"2026-07-21T12:46:32.925Z","response":{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":null,"belongs_to_collection":null,"budget":0,"genres":[],"homepage":"","id":1734523,"imdb_id":null,"origin_country":["US"],"original_language":"en","original_title":"Pencuri Cinta Kelas Satu","overview":"# Translation  For Aisya Humaira, taking care of a baby alone after her brother and sister-in-law migrated to Dubai is an easy matter. To her, becoming a mother before her time posed no problem as long as her mommy and daddy were there to help. And she never expected that caring for the little one who missed his parents would not be as easy as she thought. Therefore, she needs to find an uncle for her nephew. But who? Zulfa, her first love, rejected her. He wants to build his career first, he said! For Amar Firzal, finding a wife is not a priority. To him, having a stable job and his own house is an achievement. And he never expected that his mother would also be influenced by the typical mother in dramas who loves to nag him to get married quickly. Every excuse she gives only goes in one ear and out the other. And finally he agreed even though he was still afraid to confess his feelings to the female colleague from his office who had a higher rank than him.","popularity":0.0071,"poster_path":"/hW3EW8keZOYECJJtwu8AdtkZ80.jpg","production_companies":[],"production_countries":[],"release_date":"2018-01-01","revenue":0,"runtime":0,"softcore":false,"spoken_languages":[],"status":"Released","tagline":"","title":"Pencuri Cinta Kelas Satu","video":false,"vote_average":0,"vote_count":0,"alternative_titles":{"titles":[]},"credits":{"cast":[{"adult":false,"gender":0,"id":1616828,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Hafreez Adam","original_name":"Hafreez Adam","popularity":0.3797,"profile_path":"/bMdIwbj8hLD6EYeU1oVLUZxCanx.jpg","cast_id":2,"character":"","credit_id":"6a5e11ae900fc59472eb4a40","order":0},{"adult":false,"gender":1,"id":1449514,"known_for_department":"Acting","nam